title: BRIEF-Phillips 66 Partners Reports Q1 Earnings Per Share $0.87
text:
12 AM / Updated 11 minutes ago BRIEF-Phillips 66 Partners Reports Q1 Earnings Per Share $0.87 Reuters Staff
April 27 (Reuters) - Phillips 66 Partners LP:
* PHILLIPS 66 PARTNERS REPORTS FIRST-QUARTER 2018 EARNINGS * Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.87
* Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.86 — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* QTRLY TOTAL REVENUES AND OTHER INCOME $355 MILLION VERSUS $331 MILLION IN Q4 * Q1 REVENUE VIEW $321.3 MILLION — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* WILL CONTINUE TO FUND ORGANIC PROJECTS IN 2018 WITH CASH ON HAND, DEBT CAPACITY AND SELECTIVE USE OF ATM PROGRAM Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
